# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:42
translate spanish hwb_s11_b81aee7c:

    # "Inside the RV once again, I crash down into the driver’s seat and kick my feet up on the dash. It’s a relief to sit on something soft."
    "De vuelta dentro de la casa rodante, me dejo caer en el asiento del conductor y pongo los pies en el tablero. Es un alivio sentarme en algo suave."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:44
translate spanish hwb_s11_59213d5c:

    # "Like a satellite, Marina hovers around me, expectant."
    "Como un satélite, Marina merodea a mi alrededor, expectante."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:50
translate spanish hwb_s11_9e038d1c:

    # Amber "So, that was a failure. Obviously."
    Amber "Итак, это был провал. Очевидно."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:54
translate spanish hwb_s11_d79a93af:

    # Marina "Do you think it might be in a different part of the canyon?"
    Marina "Ты думаешь, сокровище может быть в другой части каньона?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s11_e94b6e80:

    # Amber "Maybe, but we’re not gonna find out. We could spend days out here and not find anything."
    Amber "Возможно, но мы не собираемся это выяснять. Мы могли бы проторчать здесь несколько дней и ничего не найти."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s11_257dfa70:

    # Amber "Most likely, someone else found it before us. Maybe even before this whole treasure hunt thing started."
    Amber "Скорее всего, кто-то еще до нас нашел его. Может даже до того, как эта охота за сокровищами вообще началась."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s11_89cfaad1:

    # "She stares at the ground, then perks back up."
    "Ella mira al suelo, luego se anima de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s11_13a8e302:

    # Marina "That's okay, though! All we can do is move on."
    Marina "Ничего страшного! Все, что мы можем сделать, это продолжить поиски."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s11_8606eeb8:

    # "Reaching into the glove department, she brings out the journal and hands it to me."
    "Metiendo la mano en la guantera, saca el diario y me lo entrega."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s11_f4a22767:

    # Marina "C'mon. Show me why the Human Travel Guide is the best."
    Marina "Давай-ка. Покажи мне, что Эмбер-Путеводитель лучшая."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s11_d1b63c82:

    # "I look at her for a moment, then with a smile, gently take it from her."
    "La miro por un momento, luego, con una sonrisa, lo tomo suavemente de sus manos."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s11_5b44005c:

    # Amber "Sure thing."
    Amber "Тут и сомнений быть не может."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s11_d38e74ea:

    # Amber "But that's the first and only time you're ever gonna call me that, okay?"
    Amber "Но это первый и последний раз, когда ты называешь меня так, хорошо?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s11_483376b4:

    # Marina "'Kaaaaaaay."
    Marina "Лаааадно."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s11_b7bde3d7:

    # "I flip through the journal and skim the pages. I skipped one of the entries last time because it looked like a jumbled puzzle. But if we're going to find the rest of the treasure, then we need to tackle this head on."
    "Hojeo el diario y repaso las páginas. Me salté una de las entradas la última vez porque parecía un rompecabezas enredado. Pero si vamos a encontrar el resto del tesoro, tenemos que enfrentar esto de frente."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s11_e356f684:

    # "Bracing myself for the confusion, I find the entry and groan."
    "Preparándome para la confusión, encuentro la entrada y gimo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s11_bf80318b:

    # Amber "Oh no."
    Amber "О нет."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s11_62bbad34:

    # Marina "Oh no? Does that mean you don't know where it's at?"
    Marina "О нет? Это значит, что ты не знаешь, где это находится?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s11_098bf5ae:

    # Amber "The opposite. I know exactly where it's at."
    Amber "Как раз наоборот. Я точно знаю, где это."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s11_770c2b2b:

    # Marina "Then what's the problem?"
    Marina "Тогда в чем проблема?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s11_12dc6731:

    # "I lean back in the chair and look at the ceiling."
    "Me recuesto en la silla y miro al techo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s11_1eafb19a:

    # Amber "It's in Arches National Park."
    Amber "Это в Национальном парке Арчес."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s11_861119d4:

    # Marina "Cool! Then let's go!"
    Marina "Клево! Тогда отправляемся!"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s11_2f4ed2f3:

    # "I ignore her and keep looking at the ceiling."
    "La ignoro y sigo mirando al techo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s11_7db24ce7:

    # Amber "Arches has over two-thousand natural stone arches. The miner said he hid it between two stones."
    Amber "В парке Арчес больше двух тысяч природных каменных арок. Старатель сказал, что спрятал сокровище между двумя камнями."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s11_910aad9c:

    # "She blinks. I sigh."
    "Ella parpadea. Yo suspiro."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s11_bf10de9f:

    # Amber "An arch is a rock formation that curves in the air. Think of it like an upside down {i}U{/i}."
    Amber "Арка - это каменная структура, изгибающаяся в воздухе. Считай это перевернутой буквой U."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s11_38470a18:

    # "Finally she gets the message. Her face morphs into a blank canvas and she stares out the windshield."
    "Finalmente capta el mensaje. Su rostro se transforma en un lienzo en blanco y mira fijamente por el parabrisas."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s11_ed26cac3:

    # Marina "Oh no."
    Marina "О нет."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s11_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s11_6a8b738c:

    # Amber "If we wanna find this thing, then we need to look between every single arch in Arches."
    Amber "Если мы хотим найти эту штуку, нам нужно заглянуть под каждую арку в парке."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s11_74100ed9:

    # "After a moment of petrified silence, Marina takes back the journal and returns it to its proper place in the glove department."
    "Después de un momento de silencio petrificado, Marina toma el diario y lo devuelve a su lugar adecuado en la guantera."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s11_a9b7b58b:

    # "With a shakey smile, Marina looks back at me and tries blowing it off."
    "Con una sonrisa temblorosa, Marina me mira de nuevo e intenta restarle importancia."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s11_66abd8e2:

    # Marina "A-Arches National Park, huh? It's somewhere in Moab, right? You ever been?"
    Marina "Нац-национальный парк Арчес, хм? Это где-то в Моабе, верно? Ты когда-нибудь там была?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s11_c4610c02:

    # "With a shakey grin of my own, I respond, totally ignoring the impossible feat ahead of us."
    "Con una sonrisa temblorosa propia, respondo, ignorando por completo la hazaña imposible que tenemos por delante."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s11_1ea4b2ca:

    # Amber "Y-Yeah. I went to Moab a long time ago. Arches is really famous. Like, world famous."
    Amber "Д-да. Я давно была в Моабе. Парк Арчес по-настоящему популярен. Во всем мире."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s11_8e46b38d:

    # "We're both sweating, staring at the long road ahead as we try our best to make casual conversation. It's like a game of chicken. Who's going to break first?"
    "Ambas estamos sudando, mirando el largo camino por delante mientras hacemos lo posible por mantener una conversación casual. Es como un juego del gallina. ¿Quién se rendirá primero?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s11_233bdbc0:

    # Marina "I’ve always wanted to go."
    Marina "Я всегда хотела туда попасть."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s11_4a375d1a:

    # Amber "Where have you vacationed to before?"
    Amber "А куда ты раньше ездила отдыхать?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s11_fa8c12aa:

    # Marina "Honestly, nowhere. Not out of the state, at least."
    Marina "Честно говоря, никуда. Никуда за пределы штата."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s11_904dc099:

    # Amber "For real? Not even to visit family?"
    Amber "Правда? Даже чтобы навестить семью?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s11_c034965d:

    # Marina "Nuh-uh. My grandparents live in New Mexico, too. I think only my big brother has been outside of the state."
    Marina "Неа. Мои дедушка с бабушкой тоже живут в Нью-Мексико . Думаю, только мой старший брат был за границей штата."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s11_edfc6755:

    # Amber "You got any other siblings or is it just you two?"
    Amber "У тебя есть другие братья и сестрами, или вас только двое?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s11_0e493581:

    # "She shakes her head."
    "Ella niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s11_85165847:

    # Marina "There's nine of us. I’ve got two younger brothers, three older brothers, an older sister and two little sisters."
    Marina "Нас девять. У меня есть два младших брата, три старших, старшая сестра, и еще две младшие сестры."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s11_94c30ec4:

    # "I whistle."
    "Silbo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s11_5e18bb25:

    # Amber "Damn. That’s a big-ass Christmas card."
    Amber "Черт возьми. Открытки на Рождество, наверное, девать некуда."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s11_063189df:

    # Marina "Right? At some point it’s just like, \"aren’t you ever gonna stop?\""
    Marina "Вот уж точно. В какой-то момент думаешь “может быть хватит?”."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s11_2e86a265:

    # Marina "I’m almost out of fingers to count on!"
    Marina "Скоро я не смогу пересчитать их по пальцам."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s11_a1001c1b:

    # "Chuckling, I stand up and walk to the back. Marina follows behind me."
    "Riendo, me levanto y camino hacia la parte de atrás. Marina me sigue."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s11_720201b0:

    # Marina "What about you? Do you have any siblings?"
    Marina "Что насчет тебя? У тебя есть братья или сестры?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s11_dfe7ae3d:

    # Amber "Nah, just me. Otherwise they’d probably be riding around this old thing with us."
    Amber "Неа, только я.  Иначе они бы разъезжали на этом драндулете вместе с нами."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s11_2b58cab4:

    # "As I say that, I collapse down onto my bed, sprawling out. Sitting up front felt good, but this is heavenly."
    "Mientras digo eso, me desplomo en mi cama, estirándome. Sentarme al frente se sintió bien, pero esto es celestial."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s11_c589446b:

    # "The bed sinks a little as she takes a seat on its edge."
    "La cama se hunde un poco cuando ella se sienta en el borde."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s11_2c91ef7a:

    # Amber "I can’t really imagine having a single brother or sister. Definitely not eight of them."
    Amber "Я не могу представить, каково это иметь брата или сестру. Не говоря уже о девяти."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s11_590c39bc:

    # Amber "But I guess they don’t all live at home?"
    Amber "Но я полагаю, они не все живут дома."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s11_6df52c12:

    # Marina "Actually..."
    Marina "На самом деле..."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s11_ed711915:

    # Amber "You're kidding."
    Amber "Ты шутишь."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:280
translate spanish hwb_s11_5f7ec088:

    # Marina "Only one of my brothers has moved out. It’s the worst. Like, you have to make a reservation to take a shower."
    Marina "Только один мой брат съехал. Хуже всего, что тебе надо занимать очередь, чтобы принять душ."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s11_17c69c58:

    # Amber "No wonder you ran away."
    Amber "Неудивительно, что ты сбежала."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s11_65336d8a:

    # Marina "Pretty much. As soon as I finished school I was just like, \"okay, time to get out of here.\""
    Marina "Конечно. Как только я закончила обучение, я сказала себе “настало время убираться отсюда”."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s11_de8268dc:

    # Amber "How long ago was that?"
    Amber "Как давно это было?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s11_5e250752:

    # Marina "Just a couple months. Twoish."
    Marina "Пару месяцев назад."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s11_69f2909a:

    # Amber "What’d you major in?"
    Amber "А кто ты по специальности?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s11_5b48006b:

    # Marina "Huh?"
    Marina "А?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s11_7407a086:

    # Amber "Like, what’d you get your degree in?"
    Amber "Какую специальность ты получила?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s11_74c21ed7:

    # Marina "Oh. Um. Not college. High school. I just finished high school."
    Marina "Ох. Эм. Не колледж. Я закончила школу."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s11_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s11_14ae6fba:

    # "Using my elbows, I prop myself up."
    "Usando los codos, me incorporo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s11_e0508e49:

    # Marina "What?"
    Marina "А что?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s11_f36528fd:

    # Amber "Uh, how old are you?"
    Amber "Сколько тебе лет?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s11_fd15032f:

    # "Putting her hands on her hips, Marina puffs out her cheeks and looks offended."
    "Poniendo las manos en las caderas, Marina infla las mejillas y parece ofendida."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s11_985bb993:

    # Marina "I’ll have you know it’s very rude to ask a lady her age!"
    Marina "Это довольно грубо, спрашивать леди о ее возрасте!"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s11_08de0767:

    # "She deflates."
    "Se desinfla."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s11_1025e6b9:

    # Marina "But I’m eighteen. Why?"
    Marina "Но мне восемнадцать. Почему ты спрашиваешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s11_df0fbb39:

    # Amber "Oh thank god."
    Amber "Слава богу."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s11_d14d5d05:

    # "I let myself fall back again."
    "Me dejo caer hacia atras de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s11_fd57b7bf:

    # Amber "I was afraid you were gonna be underage and that I’d get arrested for kidnapping or something."
    Amber "Я испугалась того, что ты несовершеннолетняя, и меня могут арестовать за похищение детей или что-то типа того."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s11_4ab7315a:

    # Amber "Also, I was kind of planning to go down on you at some point down the road, and that would end poorly for everyone reading as well."
    Amber "Также, я уже подумывала о том, чтобы наброситься на тебя где-нибудь в подворотне, и тогда бы меня обвинили в педофилии."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:351
translate spanish hwb_s11_1c3904a6:

    # Marina "No way! And besides, I told you my parents were fine with it. Well, accepted it."
    Marina "Ни за что! И я же тебе говорила, что родители нормально к этому отнеслись. Ну, они это приняли."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s11_a4e4a535:

    # Amber "Which part, the kidnapping or the statutory rape?"
    Amber "К какой части они отнеслись нормально, к похищению или изнасилованию несовершеннолетних?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s11_76d31925:

    # Marina "I guess both?"
    Marina "Я полагаю к обеим?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s11_12361fe4:

    # Marina "What about you? How old are you?"
    Marina "А что насчет тебя? Сколько тебе лет?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s11_dca1d09b:

    # Amber "Just a year older."
    Amber "На год старше."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:370
translate spanish hwb_s11_f2aed995:

    # Marina "Wait, you’re only nineteen?"
    Marina "Погоди, так тебе девятнадцать?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s11_51de26be:

    # "Now it’s her turn to be shocked."
    "Ahora es su turno de sorprenderse."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s11_67968b38:

    # Amber "How old did you think I was?"
    Amber "А сколько, ты думала, мне лет?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s11_4760198b:

    # "Marina busts up laughing. I’m actually a little bit embarrassed. I look away, blowing my hair from my face."
    "Marina se desternilla de risa. En realidad estoy un poco avergonzada. Aparto la mirada, apartando el cabello de mi cara."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:387
translate spanish hwb_s11_42ae7bbf:

    # Marina "Just kidding, just kidding! I figured you were like, my age or a bit older. Two years at the most."
    Marina "Шучу, шучу! Я думала, что ты моего возраста, может немного старше. На два года максимум."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s11_cec37716:

    # "I don’t look at her, staring at the wall."
    "No la miro, fijandome en la pared."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s11_3f07ee6a:

    # Marina "Oh come on, don’t be mad! I was just playing!"
    Marina "Перестань, не злись! Я просто дразнила тебя!"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s11_4844eb4d:

    # "All of a sudden she sounds seriously regretful. I wanna mess with her, but the puppy-dog look she gives me over her shoulder is too hard to resist."
    "De repente suena realmente arrepentida. Quiero molestarla, pero la mirada de cachorrito que me lanza por encima del hombro es demasiado dificil de resistir."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s11_3c3c0197:

    # Amber "Sorry, what? My hearing must be getting bad in my old age."
    Amber "Что прости? Слух стал подводить старушку."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s11_ed00dcf9:

    # "She throws a pillow at me from the bed beside her, and I deflect it with my arm."
    "Me lanza una almohada desde la cama a su lado, y la desvio con el brazo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s11_919091b3:

    # Marina "Good save, Granny."
    Marina "Хорошо сохранилась, бабуля."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s11_01a6cd30:

    # "Now she leans back too, staring up at the ceiling. Her hair spreads across my leg. I don’t move it."
    "Ahora ella tambien se reclina, mirando al techo. Su cabello se extiende sobre mi pierna. No lo muevo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s11_12922d47:

    # "Then, I realize that all the worry and nervousness we had about Arches is gone. Somewhere along the line we just forgot about it."
    "Entonces, me doy cuenta de que toda la preocupacion y el nerviosismo que teniamos sobre Arches ha desaparecido. En algun punto del camino simplemente lo olvidamos."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s11_a439b59a:

    # "Huh."
    "Huh."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:419
translate spanish hwb_s11_4f692174:

    # "I don’t know when we reached the point in our relationship where we can be comfortable being this close to each other. But I’m glad that we have."
    "No se cuando llegamos al punto en nuestra relacion en el que podemos sentirnos comodos estando tan cerca la una de la otra. Pero me alegra que lo hayamos hecho."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:421
translate spanish hwb_s11_93adad14:

    # "Maybe, just maybe, I’m enjoying the closeness a little too much."
    "Tal vez, solo tal vez, estoy disfrutando demasiado la cercania."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:423
translate spanish hwb_s11_84897bdf:

    # "It’s been a long time since I’ve dated someone. Gramps’ health made having a girlfriend impossible - there wasn’t time for anyone else."
    "Ha pasado mucho tiempo desde que sali con alguien. La salud del abuelo hizo imposible tener novia: no habia tiempo para nadie mas."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:425
translate spanish hwb_s11_8f334e62:

    # "Hell, I hardly had time for myself. Not that I cared. I’d do it all over again."
    "Demonios, apenas tenia tiempo para mi misma. No es que me importara. Lo haria todo de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:427
translate spanish hwb_s11_2366a049:

    # "Still, it's nice."
    "Aun asi, es agradable."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s11_0a3e5471:

    # "Having someone to talk to, so it's not just me and my thoughts."
    "Tener a alguien con quien hablar, para no estar solo con mis pensamientos."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s11_205ea8b6:

    # "Just as I'm about to settle into the mood, she sits up and stretches."
    "Justo cuando estoy a punto de acomodarme en el ambiente, ella se sienta y se estira."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s11_34c9c95c:

    # Marina "I’m pretty sleepy. Are you going to bed soon?"
    Marina "Я очень сонная. Ты собираешься ложиться спать?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s11_09741789:

    # Amber "Nah. I took a nap earlier, so I’m good. It’s only a few hours to Moab, so I’ll drive us there tonight."
    Amber "Неа. Я вздремну позже, я в порядке. До Моаба несколько часов, так что я привезу нас еще ночью."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s11_bd11414f:

    # Marina "Moab, huh..."
    Marina "Моаб, да..."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s11_4f0fc29f:

    # Amber "Well, yeah."
    Amber "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s11_3437e4c3:

    # Amber "Something wrong?"
    Amber "Что-то не так?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s11_7aee44fa:

    # Marina "No, I was just kinda wondering…"
    Marina "Нет, мне просто интересно..."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s11_a127a50f:

    # "She trails off."
    "Su voz se desvanece."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s11_8c01959a:

    # Amber "Wondering…?"
    Amber "Интересно?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s11_0aa7f09c:

    # Marina "Um, how far away is the Grand Canyon?"
    Marina "Эм, как мы далеко от Гранд Каньона?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s11_e6cff45c:

    # Amber "From here? I dunno, three or four hours. But it’s in the total opposite direction that we’re going."
    Amber "Отсюда? Я не знаю, три или четыре часа. Но это совершенно в другом направлении."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s11_a0fe6384:

    # Marina "Oh. Okay."
    Marina "Ох. хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:470
translate spanish hwb_s11_194f095e:

    # "The crestfallen look on her face should be illegal."
    "La mirada abatida en su rostro deberia ser ilegal."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:472
translate spanish hwb_s11_27781cb0:

    # Marina "Sorry, I should’ve looked at the map before I asked."
    Marina "Извини, я должна была посмотреть на карту, прежде чем спрашивать."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s11_87216248:

    # "Smiling, she turns and heads for bed, disappointment clinging to her like perfume."
    "Sonriendo, se da la vuelta y se dirige a la cama, con la decepcion aferrada a ella como perfume."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s11_ee164983:

    # Marina "Night, Amber."
    Marina "Спокойной ночи, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s11_a49a6ba3:

    # "Leaning against my pillows, I watch as she slowly trods off to the back."
    "Recostada contra mis almohadas, la veo mientras camina lentamente hacia el fondo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s11_f6b7a686:

    # "Come on now, I’m not {i}that{/i} heartless."
    "Vamos, no soy {i}tan{/i} desalmada."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s11_b48695c4:

    # Amber "Wait a sec."
    Amber "Подожди."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s11_2488de2c:

    # "She freezes, mid-step."
    "Se congela, a medio paso."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s11_09423d16:

    # Amber "I guess since I was gonna drive all night anyway, we can make a detour."
    Amber "Поскольку я собираюсь ехать всю ночь, мы можем сделать небольшой крюк."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s11_3af0163a:

    # Amber "A pretty big detour, too. So don’t blame me if all the treasure is gone by the time we’re done."
    Amber "И очень большой тоже. Так что не вини меня, если сокровище пропадет за время нашего отсутствия."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:501
translate spanish hwb_s11_cbb74c25:

    # "She turns around, hope springing in her face now."
    "Se da la vuelta, con esperanza brotando en su rostro ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s11_1dd52f56:

    # Amber "But I guess it is like a requirement that you see the Grand Canyon when you’re sightseeing in Arizona, so that’s what we’ll do."
    Amber "Я думаю, что грех не посетить Гранд-Каньон находясь в Аризоне."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:507
translate spanish hwb_s11_1a825846:

    # Amber "You've got a lot of vacations to make up for."
    Amber "Компенсируем твои пропущенные поездки."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s11_a99a59ef:

    # "All of the tiredness and disappointment vanishes in an instant. Like a bird taking flight, she hurries back over to where I’m just standing up."
    "Todo el cansancio y la decepción desaparecen en un instante. Como un pájaro alzando el vuelo, se apresura de vuelta hacia donde apenas me estoy levantando."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:515
translate spanish hwb_s11_79c2e1ba:

    # "A trademark Marina crash-tackle-hug knocks me onto my butt and bed again. I pat her on the back a couple times before she rises."
    "Un abrazo-choque-tackle característico de Marina me tira al suelo y a la cama otra vez. Le doy un par de palmadas en la espalda antes de que se levante."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s11_8a16ad5e:

    # Marina "Have I ever told you you’re the best?"
    Marina "Я тебе когда-нибудь говорила, что ты лучшая?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:524
translate spanish hwb_s11_4bd68572:

    # Amber "Probably. But don’t you forget it."
    Amber "Возможно. Но не забывай это."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s11_97bade3d:

    # Marina "I couldn’t if I tried!"
    Marina "Я не смогу, даже если захочу!"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:528
translate spanish hwb_s11_f46e244d:

    # Amber "Goof."
    Amber "Глупышка."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:543
translate spanish hwb_s11_f0724703:

    # "I poke her in the belly as I make my way up to the front again."
    "Le pincho la barriga mientras vuelvo a subir al frente."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:547
translate spanish hwb_s11_a55cfccf:

    # Amber "Grab me an energy drink from the fridge, will you?"
    Amber "Подай мне энергетик из холодильника, пожалуйста."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:581
translate spanish hwb_s11_30dfea35:

    # "When she sits down in the passenger seat, she has two cans of the energy drink."
    "Cuando se sienta en el asiento del pasajero, tiene dos latas de la bebida energética."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:583
translate spanish hwb_s11_ed185598:

    # Amber "Thought you were going to bed?"
    Amber "Я думала, ты собиралась спать?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:587
translate spanish hwb_s11_bee3c3d1:

    # Marina "No way! I’m too excited now! I’ll keep you company on the drive."
    Marina "Ни за что! Теперь я слишком взволнована! Я составлю тебе компанию на время пути."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:591
translate spanish hwb_s11_eca3bcda:

    # Marina "Plus, it’s only like 8 o’clock isn’t it?"
    Marina "Тем более сейчас только 8 часов, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:595
translate spanish hwb_s11_c2ecbe0f:

    # Amber "Beats me. Sounds right."
    Amber "Понятия не имею. Но наверное так."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:597
translate spanish hwb_s11_a5d10d98:

    # "I pop open the tab on my drink and take a long draught. It tastes awful, but it wakes me up like nothing else. I guess the makers cut out sweeteners and nice flavors for more stimulants."
    "Abro la pestaña de mi bebida y tomo un largo trago. Sabe horrible, pero me despierta como nada más. Supongo que los fabricantes eliminaron los edulcorantes y sabores agradables por más estimulantes."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:599
translate spanish hwb_s11_773ff7f1:

    # "To drink it faster, I hold my breath to hide the taste and chug."
    "Para beberlo más rápido, aguanto la respiración para ocultar el sabor y lo tomo de un tirón."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:601
translate spanish hwb_s11_ba32dee2:

    # "Gasping, I crumple the empty can and toss it into a trash bag. Marina, on the other hand, sips it daintily, wincing each time."
    "Jadeando, estrujo la lata vacía y la tiro a una bolsa de basura. Marina, por otro lado, lo bebe a sorbos con delicadeza, haciendo una mueca cada vez."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:605
translate spanish hwb_s11_3d6b94bb:

    # Marina "People seriously drink this stuff?"
    Marina "Люди реально пьют эту гадость?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:607
translate spanish hwb_s11_6038eb55:

    # Amber "Somehow. It works though. It’s pretty much the strongest stuff you can get without a prescription."
    Amber "Ну да. Надо признать он работает. Это самая мощная штука, которую можно купить без рецепта."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:609
translate spanish hwb_s11_a9ba11a6:

    # "After taking another sip, Marina retches and sticks her tongue out. She reminds me of a cat with fur stuck on its tongue."
    "Después de otro sorbo, Marina hace arcadas y saca la lengua. Me recuerda a un gato con pelo pegado en la lengua."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:611
translate spanish hwb_s11_e1e76a12:

    # "She sets the can in the cup holder beside me."
    "Deja la lata en el portavasos a mi lado."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:613
translate spanish hwb_s11_5543a17d:

    # Marina "Do you want mine? I can’t drink this."
    Marina "Не хочешь допить мой? Я больше не могу."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:617
translate spanish hwb_s11_1c481997:

    # Amber "I’d have a heart attack if I drank two. Just leave it and I’ll drink it tomorrow."
    Amber "У меня будет сердечный приступ, если выпью две. Просто оставь, я выпью завтра."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:619
translate spanish hwb_s11_10d8e7e6:

    # "Because the only way to improve an awful energy drink is to let it get warm and flat."
    "Porque la única forma de mejorar una bebida energética horrible es dejarla que se entibie y se vuelva plana."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:623
translate spanish hwb_s11_2f2b41bc:

    # "As I start the RV, Marina says something, but it’s soft enough that I can’t hear her over the engine revving."
    "Mientras enciendo la casa rodante, Marina dice algo, pero es tan suave que no la oigo por el rugido del motor."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:625
translate spanish hwb_s11_3cad5ff1:

    # Amber "What was that? Old lady hearing failing on me again."
    Amber "Что ты сказала? Слух снова подводит старушку."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:630
translate spanish hwb_s11_ce83ce9c:

    # "Smiling, she shakes her head."
    "Sonriendo, niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:632
translate spanish hwb_s11_470dbec3:

    # Marina "I was just saying ‘thanks’ again."
    Marina "Я еще раз сказала спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:634
translate spanish hwb_s11_eb012488:

    # Amber "Don’t thank me yet. I could fall asleep at the wheel and kill us both."
    Amber "Пока не благодари. Я могу уснуть за рулем и угробить нас."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:638
translate spanish hwb_s11_e4aaa924:

    # Marina "At least I’d die happy!"
    Marina "По крайней мере, умру счастливой!"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:642
translate spanish hwb_s11_55392769:

    # Marina "No though, not just that. For taking me with you and doing the treasure hunt and everything."
    Marina "Нет, не так. Я хочу поблагодарить тебя за то, что взяла меня с собой, за эту охоту за сокровищами, и за все."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s11_21e407b2:

    # Amber "You must be super tired. You’re saying all sorts of weird stuff now."
    Amber "Ты, должно быть, очень устала. Сейчас ты сказала все странные вещи, которые только могла."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:650
translate spanish hwb_s11_6effb033:

    # Marina "I mean it! I know it’s kind of random. I’m just really happy I met you."
    Marina "Я серьезно! Я знаю, что все это вышло случайно. И я действительно счастлива, что повстречала тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s11_d1956022:

    # "After a moment of blushing, I laugh a little under my breath."
    "Después de un momento de sonrojarme, me río un poco en voz baja."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s11_cd30718e:

    # Amber "Yeah, me too."
    Amber "Ага, я тоже."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:672
translate spanish hwb_s11_a3d402d5:

    # "I prevent any more cheesy conversation by carefully pulling out of the parking lot and back onto the exit road."
    "Evito cualquier conversación empalagosa saliendo con cuidado del estacionamiento y de vuelta a la carretera de salida."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:674
translate spanish hwb_s11_2375fdf0:

    # "I’m definitely glad that Marina’s enjoying herself. I’m having fun, too. But talking about that sort of thing… It makes me feel all squirmy inside."
    "Definitivamente me alegra que Marina se esté divirtiendo. Yo también me estoy divirtiendo. Pero hablar de ese tipo de cosas... Me hace sentir toda inquieta por dentro."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:676
translate spanish hwb_s11_69e6349f:

    # "Like I don’t match up to what Marina thinks of me."
    "Como si no estuviera a la altura de lo que Marina piensa de mí."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:678
translate spanish hwb_s11_ef6d2912:

    # "Pushing those thoughts out of my head, I focus on the road."
    "Sacando esos pensamientos de mi cabeza, me concentro en la carretera."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:680
translate spanish hwb_s11_62ac24ea:

    # "We have to keep our eyes peeled for animals out here. There are lots of stray dogs in this part of the state, and dozens of deer and antelope just waiting to race cars."
    "Tenemos que mantener los ojos bien abiertos por los animales aquí. Hay muchos perros callejeros en esta parte del estado, y docenas de ciervos y antílopes esperando para correr con los autos."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:682
translate spanish hwb_s11_cb23f25f:

    # "The road’s devoid of other vehicles, though. And since I know the exits to take, more or less, we should make pretty good time."
    "La carretera está desierta de otros vehículos, sin embargo. Y como sé más o menos las salidas que tomar, deberíamos avanzar bastante rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:684
translate spanish hwb_s11_c81cf30d:

    # "Once we get back onto the highway, Marina hoists the bucket of tapes onto her lap."
    "Una vez que volvemos a la autopista, Marina levanta el cubo de cintas sobre su regazo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:688
translate spanish hwb_s11_65100bc0:

    # Marina "What do you wanna listen to?"
    Marina "Что ты хочешь послушать?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:692
translate spanish hwb_s11_20e84360:

    # Amber "Hmm…"
    Amber "Хммм."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:694
translate spanish hwb_s11_3ef3a635:

    # "I glance between the road and the bin, scanning both."
    "Miro entre la carretera y el contenedor, escaneando ambos."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:698
translate spanish hwb_s11_9bd839f3:

    # "I settle on an album that I haven’t had the heart to listen to in a while. But it feels like tonight is the right time."
    "Me decido por un álbum que no he tenido el corazón de escuchar en un tiempo. Pero siento que esta noche es el momento adecuado."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:702
translate spanish hwb_s11_7b0aa655:

    # "I fish out the tape and slide it into the player. As the first chords start up, I watch Marina’s face for a reaction."
    "Saco la cinta y la deslizo en el reproductor. Mientras suenan los primeros acordes, observo el rostro de Marina en busca de una reacción."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:706
translate spanish hwb_s11_940f400d:

    # "It won’t have the same sentimental value to her, I know, but it’s an emotional album in general. Lots of dynamics to the music and simple but heartfelt songwriting."
    "No tendrá el mismo valor sentimental para ella, lo sé, pero es un álbum emotivo en general. Mucha dinámica en la música y composiciones simples pero sinceras."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:708
translate spanish hwb_s11_0d54f231:

    # "Gramps used to try to play along, but said he couldn’t quite capture the feeling himself."
    "El abuelo solía intentar tocar junto, pero decía que no lograba capturar bien el sentimiento."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:712
translate spanish hwb_s11_a8e2de2e:

    # "As I’d hoped, Marina’s quiet. Which means that she’s listening. Her cheek is pressed against the window again."
    "Como esperaba, Marina está callada. Lo que significa que está escuchando. Tiene la mejilla apoyada contra la ventana otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:714
translate spanish hwb_s11_2aed00b2:

    # "Her reflection, barely visible, looks wistful."
    "Su reflejo, apenas visible, se ve melancólico."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:716
translate spanish hwb_s11_c5fa6fdf:

    # "Good."
    "Bien."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:720
translate spanish hwb_s11_7209c17c:

    # "For the second time today, a growing pressure starts in my eyes. I paw at them, and the motion catches Marina’s attention."
    "Por segunda vez hoy, siento una presión creciente en los ojos. Me los froto, y el movimiento llama la atención de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:724
translate spanish hwb_s11_70bec10c:

    # Marina "You sure you’re not too tired?"
    Marina "Ты уверена, что не слишком устала?"

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s11_24c727d0:

    # Amber "Oh, yeah. Eyes are just a little itchy."
    Amber "О да. Глаза просто немного слезятся."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:730
translate spanish hwb_s11_59f1bbbe:

    # "Dammit. My voice shakes as I speak. But if she notices, she doesn’t say anything."
    "Maldición. Mi voz tiembla mientras hablo. Pero si lo nota, no dice nada."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:732
translate spanish hwb_s11_f6ff49f5:

    # "This album was another one Gramps’ favorites, and there’s a reason I haven’t listened to it since he passed. Turning it on might have been a mistake."
    "Este álbum era otro de los favoritos del abuelo, y hay una razón por la que no lo he escuchado desde que falleció. Ponerlo quizás fue un error."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:734
translate spanish hwb_s11_145859a5:

    # "We may yet go off the road if I end up crying. Or I might just die of embarrassment."
    "Podríamos terminar fuera de la carretera si termino llorando. O quizás muera de vergüenza."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:736
translate spanish hwb_s11_37d448ce:

    # "I sniffle a couple times to keep myself under control."
    "Sorbo un par de veces para mantenerme bajo control."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:738
translate spanish hwb_s11_089625ad:

    # Amber "Damn allergies."
    Amber "Проклятая аллергия."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:740
translate spanish hwb_s11_c118736a:

    # "I don’t even know if she hears me."
    "Ni siquiera sé si me escucha."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:742
translate spanish hwb_s11_cc3c9871:

    # "I’m kind of tempted to turn it off, and play something else. But I want Marina to hear it."
    "Tengo la tentación de apagarlo y poner otra cosa. Pero quiero que Marina lo escuche."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:744
translate spanish hwb_s11_789122c5:

    # "It won’t mean anything special to her, I’m sure. I want to see what she thinks. To see if maybe Gramps and I were crazy, or if there was more to the music and the man playing it."
    "No significará nada especial para ella, estoy segura. Quiero ver qué opina. Para ver si quizás el abuelo y yo estábamos locos, o si había algo más en la música y el hombre que la tocaba."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:746
translate spanish hwb_s11_a433a8e0:

    # "He was a guitarist and songwriter who just went by the name of June."
    "Era un guitarrista y compositor que solo se hacía llamar June."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:748
translate spanish hwb_s11_8efaa0d9:

    # "Died a few years ago."
    "Murió hace unos años."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:750
translate spanish hwb_s11_c12e9bae:

    # "Fighting back the nostalgia and the bubbling feelings of how much I miss Gramps is hard. I’m able to hold on, though, and keep from breaking down."
    "Contener la nostalgia y los sentimientos burbujeantes de cuánto extraño al abuelo es difícil. Pero logro aguantar y no derrumbarme."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:754
translate spanish hwb_s11_9ac9f47a:

    # "Forty-five minutes later, when the tape ends, Marina hits the play button again to start it over."
    "Cuarenta y cinco minutos después, cuando termina la cinta, Marina presiona el botón de reproducción otra vez para empezarla de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:756
translate spanish hwb_s11_78dff3d5:

    # "I’d say it was worth it."
    "Diría que valió la pena."

# game/script/hwb_s11.rpy:760
translate spanish hwb_s11_cd1effbe:

    # "I let it play on for hours, long after Marina’s fallen asleep beside me."
    "La dejo sonar durante horas, mucho después de que Marina se haya quedado dormida a mi lado."

